<% title "Scholarship Database | OMSFA | University of Washington" %>

<div class="card content" style="padding-bottom: 0px">
	<h5><%= link_to "Office of Merit Scholarships, Fellowships & Awards: Scholarships Search", scholarships_path %></h5>

	<div class="row">
	  <%= search_form_for @search do |f| %>
			<div class="input-field col s5">
				<%= f.search_field :title_or_description_or_history_or_eligibility_cont, :placeholder => "Type keywords (one keyword at a time)" %>			
			</div>
			<div class="input-field col s3">
				<%= f.button type: :submit, :class => 'btn waves-effect waves-light' do %>
						<i class="material-icons left">search</i>Search
					<% end %>
			</div>			
	  <% end %>
	</div>
	
</div>

<ul class="collapsible">	
  <li>
		<div class="collapsible-header"><span class='mi uw_purple'>info</span> Tips for Searching for Scholarships in Our Database <i class="mi iconcollapse">expand_more</i></div>
	    <div class="collapsible-body">	    	
				<p>•  Not sure what keywords to use? Check out our <a href='https://scholarships.uw.edu/get-started/planning/' target="_blank">tips for preparing your search</a>.</p>
		 		<p>•  Want a starting point list to jumpstart your search? Try our <a href='https://scholarships.uw.edu/search/guides/' target="_blank">scholarship guides</a>.</p>		 	 		
		 		<p>•  Search in multiple databases to find a wider range of scholarships. <a href='https://scholarships.uw.edu/search/searching-for-scholarships-tools-strategies/' target="_blank">Additional scholarship search tools to try</a>.</p>

			<i>Using keywords:</i> Each scholarship you apply for might be a good fit for you in a different way. We recommend searching for one keyword at a time. Consider keywords related to your: academic and professional fields of interest, future goals, activities you enjoy, issues you care about, communities you are part of, and identities you hold.

			<p><i>Using filters:</i> The filters will restrict your results to show only scholarships that include ALL the criteria you selected. </p>

			<p>If you want to exclude scholarships in a given category to avoid results for which you will NOT be eligible (i.e. you are not a Washington resident), then make that selection and leave it on for all searches. </p>

			<p>As you search, also look for additional search resources/websites/databases based on:</p>
					<p>•  identities you hold,</p>
					<p>•  communities you belong to,</p>
					<p>•  values you have, and</p>
					<p>•  campus resources that provide you specific guidance.</p>

					<p>Although we're not able to list those resources here, there are many excellent databases and search sites available that you can do a targeted search for based on those identities, communities, etc. relevant for you.</p>

			<p>Found all the relevant scholarships on our database? Check out other databases! We can’t list every scholarship out there, so it’s good to check out a few different <a href="https://scholarships.uw.edu/search/searching-for-scholarships-tools-strategies/" target="_blank">search platforms</a>.</p>
	    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

<%= render 'results' %>
<% sidebar :filters %>
<br>
<small>Any problems or questions about this scholarship search should be sent to <%= auto_link(Unit.find_by_abbreviation('omsfa').email) %>.</small>